                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-21585",
                            "title": "User interface improvements",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-21585\" target=\"_blank\">XT-21585</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<ul><li>On the\u00a0<b>Customer</b>\u00a0page, you can find the\u00a0<b>Minimum order amount</b>\u00a0field on the\u00a0<b>Financial</b>\u00a0tab.</li><li><b>Sales shipment</b>,\u00a0<b>Sales invoice</b>, and\u00a0<b>Sales credit memo</b>\u00a0reports are available in English.</li></ul>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "group",
                    "title": "Improvements",
                    "taxonomies": {
                        "_type": [
                            "changes"
                        ]
                    },
                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-24708",
                            "title": "Assign sequence numbers ",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-24708\" target=\"_blank\">XT-24708</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>The\u00a0<b>Sequence number assignment</b> page includes <b>Sales</b>,\u00a0<b>Purchasing</b>,\u00a0<b>Stock</b>, and\u00a0<b>Manufacturing</b>\u00a0menus and the related documents. Each document has a default sequence number assigned to it.</p><p>In the side panel, the\u00a0<b>Assign on posting</b>\u00a0checkbox displays when the\u00a0<b>Sales invoice</b> document type and French legislation are selected. When selected, the sequence number is assigned when posted.</p><p>The value of the\u00a0<b>Sequence number value</b> field on the\u00a0<b>Company</b>\u00a0and\u00a0<b>Site</b> pages is employed to generate document numbers when the related sequence number uses a site or company component.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "title": "Distribution",
            "id": "distribution",
            "type": "module",
            "content_parts": [
