                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-25436",
                            "title": "Returns are valued at the original receipt or delivery cost",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-25436\" target=\"_blank\">XT-25436</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>For sales returns, the returned stock is valued at the original delivery cost and not at the current cost. For purchase returns, the returned stock is valued at the original receipt cost and not at the current cost.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-7520",
                            "title": "Stock detail status in stock entry transactions",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-7520\" target=\"_blank\">XT-7520</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>You can see the current status of the stock detail entry in the <b>Stock detail status</b> column in functions with stock movements.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-6967",
                            "title": "Managing non-stock items",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-6967\" target=\"_blank\">XT-6967</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>In the <b>Item-site</b> function, stock related fields do not display for non-stock managed items or for items with a <b>Service</b> item type. In the sales and purchase process, the following controls are performed: </p><ul><li>You can use these items only if they are linked to a stock site.</li><li>You cannot link a stock managed item to a non-stock site.</li></ul><p>\u00a0</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-6878",
                            "title": "Managing non-stock items in the purchase process",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-6878\" target=\"_blank\">XT-6878</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>In the purchase document lines and on the edit and detail panels, you can select, display, and manage items that are not stock managed.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "20.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
