                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "For Material tracking, the item search criteria has been renamed to &quot;Released item&quot; and the component item and material columns have been renamed to &quot;Component.&quot;<br/>For Time tracking, &quot;Released item&quot; columns have been added.<br/>For Production tracking, &quot;Released item&quot; search criteria has been added and the item columns have been renamed to &quot;Released item.&quot;",
