                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>On the <b>Notification history</b> page, you can view the notification history for integrations and services. This helps you identify errors and assist in finding resolutions.</p><p>You can access this function from the <b>Administration &gt; Communication</b> menu.</p>",
